# Mappls (MapMyIndia) Web Map SDK key — enables the LIVE basemap + patrol route.
# Get it from apis.mappls.com/console → your project → "REST / Map SDK Key" → Default Key.
#
# This is a PUBLIC client key (it ships inside the static bundle, like a Google Maps key),
# so BEFORE deploying, restrict it by domain in the console (Whitelisted Domains).
# Do NOT put the Client Secret here — it must never reach client-side code.
# Without this key the app falls back to the crash-proof schematic map automatically.
#
# To enable: copy this file to ".env" (same folder) and paste your Map SDK key:
VITE_MAPPLS_KEY=
